column.name: content
column.value:
We are extremely lucky and pleased to introduce the highly renowned celebrity chef Francois Curie into our kitchen for 4 special gourmet evenings. Francois has created a unique 3-course dinner over the theme Golf & Forest for this occasion. The menu consists of

 

 

Brestogne Cream Mushroom Soup

Roasted Phesant with Cranberry Sauce and Roasted Sweet Potato

Petit Fours with Coffee and Tea ad libitum

 

The price for this spectacular evening is £69 and there are a limited number of spaces available. Dates and times will be announced later, but to make a prelimenary booking please call us.
